{"tid":1451700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真三罷】何韻詩：呼籲各界長期罷工","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:16:27.000Z","uid":15846,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3e2447a1474558b3e55daa66455478699bde7d","tid":1451700,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:16.000Z","msg":"Link：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100375550229/posts/10162274768180230?s=100000644320275&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100375550229%2Fposts%2F10162274768180230%3Fs%3D100000644320275%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=1fa57008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100375550229/posts/10162274768180230?s=100000644320275&amp;sfns=xmo</a><br />\n<br />\n呼籲全港所有有影響力嘅行業同工會，例如公務員、航空界、運輸界、教育界等等，認真部署一次長期罷工罷市罷買（再落去甚至要罷交租罷交稅）。唔係求求其其罷一兩日，而係一個認真嘅長時間嘅大型行動。因為，再咁落去，你地保得住自己份工，都再保唔住我地嘅香港。只有當足夠嘅人向政府真正施壓，我地先可以見到轉機。<br />\n<br />\n出於人道理由，出於為已經犧牲甚多嘅前線接力嘅理由，出於唔想再有更多人受傷被捕、出於為我地嘅城市搵返真正公義嘅理由，希望各行各業嘅你，認真同你地嘅業界研究討論一下，並且要快，喺短時間內可以集體進行。<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，無得再等，真係到咗和理非終極接力嘅時候喇。<br />\n<br />\n我地每一個都做得到。"},{"pid":"04c785d2d7ee4855b95555788ad77387b4ea1643","tid":1451700,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:59.000Z","msg":"罷工！"},{"pid":"ca117e196a359b6c48ab679f6c58c0c0083aadc0","tid":1451700,"uid":301676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:09:43.000Z","msg":"警黑還眼<br />\n百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSbwbAZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSbwbAZ.png&h=de534a44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZfADf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZfADf0.png&h=493e7fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKXSFup.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKXSFup.png&h=df4f59aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7504110742f73bfc20db921f624891252c282b96","tid":1451700,"uid":15846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:13.000Z","msg":"真三罷，唔係射波"},{"pid":"8333efbeee4ddca48bb8f66781599024cecb6081","tid":1451700,"uid":187510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:44.000Z","msg":"HOCC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c52c51021f741caa80995179fdb9f79f664663","tid":1451700,"uid":269975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-tWasHlig5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-tWasHlig5s&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=f91cde4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-tWasHlig5s</a><br />\n推到黑警仆街為止"},{"pid":"27f82f84bda845b0b936952a5f84547d8f99340a","tid":1451700,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451065/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451065/page/1</a><br />\n其實做到全民罷工一d都唔難<br />\n其實講左好多次<br />\n只要每星期搵半日下午或者lunch time<br />\n快閃中環集會(或者各上班主區分區lunch time 快閃集會)<br />\n現時情況下大家都好怕上班區會變左周末元朗大埔葵芳黃大仙北角，各公司只要有少少風吹草動都會提前比打工仔收工，店舖亦會關門，變相罷工一樣<br />\n只係唔明點解示威集會只集中周末一到平日就收皮<br />\n一星期搵半日下午甚至只係lunch time出來有咁難?<br />\n平日半日快閃集會，堅持下去自然就會變左一星期一日罷工，又簡單又易堅持落去，可以趁現在民憤大，隨時可以開始"},{"pid":"9e7f84060b2387566bd28c16a38a87ce27548498","tid":1451700,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:12:08.000Z","msg":"［文宣炸彈整合］ 8.11警察黑暗醜惡系列<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448291</a><br />\n<br />\n人人都係文宣組！文宣圖集中post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449111</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣]長輩文宣圖任攞任屌唔嬲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450443</a>"},{"pid":"8e3dfa288963048c40978dcc4808f062aff00c96","tid":1451700,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:18:10.000Z","msg":"長期罷"},{"pid":"b066fcbaf2845e300eeadb5befc682fda0a7ab3e","tid":1451700,"uid":288830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:27:38.000Z","msg":"裡邊係一啲優先唔會搞到市民嘅行動，圍機場、開放西隧大欖隧道，仲有好多好多方法！<br />\n<br />\n小妹同朋友有篇中長期戰術文有講，啱聽求幫推！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444720/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d470b06edb5f576236edc99432c92e23e7638e2d","tid":1451700,"uid":300554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"有前無後 打死罷就<br />\n<br />\n成日都話未係時機？時機就係一觸即發！已經有好充分理由無限罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9f7f68a1b715d98d1fb9851ace0a6dcbe88ba33","tid":1451700,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:49:33.000Z","msg":"三罷呀屌"},{"pid":"6b272356647a2c9779318378b8242f8e72a26baa","tid":1451700,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:28:30.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"5ba0b186985da9c5134e00bb9ff32b99a2bcaa42","tid":1451700,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c9b9aac1ffd1b9dec8cbfc7981f1b43df8bc6d4","tid":1451700,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n但無限期罷工對部分市民可能有困難"},{"pid":"7e3925c10180f5e3ddb6bfd84727f5761b8b6aad","tid":1451700,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"// 我係爆眼女義士個妹，想同大家講啲野<br />\n<br />\n首先想多謝大家關心，希望你地將呢份憤怒，帶去今日和你飛要做既事身上 塞爆香城機場<br />\n<br />\n傷勢方面：<br />\n我家姐右眼全紫 腫到雞蛋咁大 <br />\n右眼眼頭至眼袋位有好長既傷口 爛哂 <br />\n剛剛深夜縫左針<br />\n<br />\n根據醫生所講，傷勢嚴重，中彈附近既骨(鼻骨、眉骨 暫時知既係咁多）都碎哂<br />\n做左緊急手術 扶骨勉強扶到 因為多碎骨都有困難<br />\n毀容就一定<br />\n跟住就暫時連我都未知情況如何<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n暫時未有狗上門 <br />\n網上都有好多消息<br />\n所以其實好大機會狗係知我地係邊<br />\n之所以未搵上門<br />\n100%因為怕以家拉人會民 憤 升 溫！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n眾籌方面我地屋企的確有需要<br />\n好多謝大家既慷慨<br />\n詳情再向大家報告<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下落嚟<br />\n我想講下佢發夢親口同我講既事發經過：<br />\n<br />\n當時佢係尖沙咀警署外<br />\n係巴士站觀察緊狗既行動 無衝擊 無做任何攻擊性動作<br />\n<br />\n佢同我講 只係伸個頭係巴士站廣告版之間既空隙望出去 <br />\n<br />\n就有個防暴定唔知速龍係近距離<br />\n只有8-10米既距離下<br />\n開左槍 中左眼 <br />\n隨即倒地 流左好多血 口鼻都滲血<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我家姐係一個好善良既人<br />\n612發夢幫左好多人 <br />\n由一個後排幫人洗眼教人點走<br />\n由連出聲屌平時地鐵啲社會垃圾都唔敢<br />\n變成一個熱血企前線既勇士<br />\n<br />\n佢只係一個愛香港既女仔<br />\n一個想保護自己屋企<br />\n維護人性人權<br />\n為自由而戰<br />\n一個內外都靚既女仔<br />\n<br />\n黑警 你地會有報應 <br />\n惡有惡報 若然不報 時晨未到<br />\n狗共港府殺人償命<br />\n係呢一刻仲覺得唔關自己事？<br />\n<br />\n當你今天蒙蔽雙眼 <br />\n明天維穩之火會燒到你身邊<br />\n硬生生剝奪你所有自由<br />\n<br />\n你今天可以為這個為自由而戰的女生走出來嗎？<br />\n你今天可以為這個家走出來嗎？<br />\n<br />\n和理非 和你飛 <br />\n今日1點 著好裝備 香城機場見"},{"pid":"0396417e8c79e96325b306c048f81d4fe61d0ab1","tid":1451700,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"180e52b6d3d0cc6da01ae4f7f1b0e7c5518c7672","tid":1451700,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:52:18.000Z","msg":"遊客都唔走，一齊屌共狗，現場一手料！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警還眼 暴權還命</strong></span><br />\n眼啊？命啊？我哋喺機場等你還！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">明日戰士</span>們，我等緊你哋返嚟啊！<br />\n聽朝我哋搭頭班車返屋企衝涼<br />\n聽朝你哋頭班機入嚟飲個早茶<br />\n今日情緒病告假，聽日要覆診續假，後日又會復發喎⋯<br />\n正苦再唔出嚟對症下藥，後遺症手尾長啊⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>話罷就罷 不罷不休 持續咁罷 接力去罷</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015835_e4897445020a251037eb44804f80ccd7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015835_e4897445020a251037eb44804f80ccd7.jpeg&h=a6cb7d26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015836_bc541ac20754111de24ca91116926766.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015836_bc541ac20754111de24ca91116926766.jpeg&h=b6587e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015837_cfbd939f7b262d6ed4b42405eb9bb5e3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015837_cfbd939f7b262d6ed4b42405eb9bb5e3.jpeg&h=f0953262&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015839_f286e406de249e3f0f2d3dbf5ce80587.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015839_f286e406de249e3f0f2d3dbf5ce80587.jpeg&h=dc0c1fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015840_43b458b16c046d1336d2b9ba102539c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015840_43b458b16c046d1336d2b9ba102539c4.png&h=a82c02d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oqALAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oqALAZ.jpg&h=6b440aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkPqonG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkPqonG.jpg&h=5c590cba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rkheun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rkheun.jpg&h=ba41d73f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9d45e893fc683a9f7d5120452c367ff0d5fb55","tid":1451700,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"第三隻眼<br />\n<br />\n好痛<br />\n<br />\n唔想再有血案 求下大家<br />\n用盡所有力氣推持續罷工<br />\n真正實行有效有用嘅罷工<br />\n全世界放低份工保護義士<br />\n忍一時之痛 重奪主權<br />\n<br />\n好攰<br />\n政府搞到我無力返工"}]}